Unlike the recommended method in the manual this method has 100% success rate.

Steps:
1. Tighten the Resin VAT
2. Loosen the Build Plate
3. Select TOOLS --> MOVE Z--> HOME
4. Move the Build Plate till a slight contact is made with the Resin VAT using 1mm increment option
5. If the Build Plate moves freely continue to lower it using 0.1mm increment option till the movement no longer occurs.
6. Carefully tighten the Build Plate
7. Once tightened, increase the Build Plate by 0.3mm.
8. Go Back, Click --> Z=0 option to set your Z axis.
